      "content": "it does feel like a constant noise that i can't ever turn off. i try to take breaks but then the notifications come back, or i just think about what people are saying about me and i can't breathe. it feels like i'm trapped in a room where everyone is just screaming at me. i just want it to be quiet. i just want everything to stop.",
